  "description": "Large grains (0.75) at low density — you hear the silence between. Position scatter is 0.2 so the grains drift slowly across the source material. Pitch scatter nearly zero. Six-second attack, four-second release. The texture coalesces from nothing and returns to nothing. This is granular erosion, not synthesis.",
